title: greedy

description.plain:
Described as her ‘most playful’ track yet, “greedy” is a fun and upbeat self-empowering pop track that promotes self-confidence. The song details McRae telling men not to get too consumed by their interest in her, or in other words, their eponymous ‘greed’, whilst also playfully boasting how she would want herself too.

This song was first teased on August 4, 2023, before being officially released on September 15, 2023.

“greedy” is Tate’s second single to reach 1 billion streams on Spotify.
